{"tid":1069921,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"比個90後同事阻住同老細出火","createTime":"2019-03-20T09:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T15:07:02.000Z","uid":58880,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bcdafbae798503813efdd3f9068bdeb1dd6bf071","tid":1069921,"uid":58880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"話說老細最近已經好多project要跟，壓力大到仆街<br />\n<br />\n咁就比老細叫左入房幫佢出出火減下壓 ，<br />\n<br />\n一入到去就同老細做前戲，<br />\n<br />\n到老細準備出火既時候，<br />\n<br />\n點知兩個90後下屬因為叮飯而鬧交<br />\n<br />\n其中一個仲衝入黎阻撚住老細出火，<br />\n<br />\n即刻搞到我要落枱底，<br />\n<br />\n咁張枱個高度岩岩好姐住我同老細條丁個90後見唔到我，<br />\n<br />\n但係出緊火既關係老細一野射落左我塊面到，<br />\n<br />\nD精臭到仆街，<br />\n<br />\n咁呢個情況老細就係咁意叫個90後放兩日假休息下，<br />\n<br />\n個傻仔仲笑笑口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等佢走左之後我就同老細講炒左佢，<br />\n<br />\n條傻仔仲以為衝入黎好型，<br />\n<br />\n準備搵定工啦傻仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f0b208950e31b513f65cd02d9fbb7c828e8fce","tid":1069921,"uid":6248,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"👎🏻"},{"pid":"ff7af5f79d35c52e2d113754b305a615ee79b6fe","tid":1069921,"uid":110325,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:46:08.000Z","msg":"0.2/10"},{"pid":"28604d6d70510c4c63f07832ebca7546d3028ff4","tid":1069921,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦方面G"},{"pid":"68cf1a3f7c8722b6b8a8b68ea10e2b1b2dbc2691","tid":1069921,"uid":136186,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"on9 你喺枱底又見到笑笑口 作故係咪唔使合邏輯啊"},{"pid":"4cfc429d6a13cb9045ac802aed080d583988d306","tid":1069921,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"我係空氣，比你地吸撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5a